{"tid":2212244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭敬基加國被叫「小漢奸」 幸有同路人暢談政事己見","createTime":"2020-09-21T15:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T18:30:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":380,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"b76e5826067f2ef0f6866958665c26f0b527e74a","tid":2212244,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:49:26.000Z","msg":"自居「流忙歌手」的鄭敬基，於今年7月帶着母親及妻子返加拿大，並表示2020年內都不會返港，但他沒有忘記香港的手足，落力打國際線，除了與加拿大國會議員Erin Otoole見面並說明香港狀況外，又越洋支持8.27的全城黑衣日，更不時開直播與大家保持聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n鄭敬基提到，返加近3個月以來，在當地外出食飯時，遇到很多支持他的人，有些會含蓄低調地給他打氣，感謝他為香港發聲，但也有遇過嘴藐藐加擰頭，以示不同意的人，鄭敬基稱更曾遇到有人離遠叫他「小漢奸」，不過他指自己尚未發現有人跟蹤，人身尚算安全。<br />\n<br />\n鄭敬基夫婦與同路人一起吃飯時，問到如果遇到極藍人士會點算，對方稱為保幾十年的友誼，若對方不提，自己也不會主動提起，鄭敬基及太太感好奇，於是一直問下去，想知到真實原因。可惜，最後無答案，大家以苦笑一下收場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200921/BN2B7NAAOZDTTCLVJGYTJLWJSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200921%2FBN2B7NAAOZDTTCLVJGYTJLWJSM%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zES9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=20a15757\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200921%2FBN2B7NAAOZDTTCLVJGYTJLWJSM%2F&h=f3a4edf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200921/BN2B7NAAOZDTTCLVJGYTJLWJSM/</a>"},{"pid":"5991d1df48b006ab58f4ee61a08824954b2dfcea","tid":2212244,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3b69651e2d3212a8493a8713d3ea9ea37b0d52","tid":2212244,"uid":83228,"like":445,"dislike":0,"score":445,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"講人漢奸<br />\n咁你仲乜留喺加拿大<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907a6a293edb204e10a04a33b29a3f47078d4919","tid":2212244,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a